column5: Going to be up at Fisherman's Cove on the 20th of June. Anybody else going to be up there then? CAN'T WAIT!!!! Anyone have any current fishing reports from that area?
Jester we will be there the week after you so don't catch em all leave some for the rest of us!!!!
I also arrive at FC on June 27th, along with my wife and two sons. I'll look for an Indiana plate. I think we're in 3A.
Carnhzkr-dstar was mistaken. He will be there JULY 25. I know because he's my brother... My older retired brother! Lol!
Story of my life, "Alone Again, Naturally".
dang it I was trying to get up there early and my brother had to spoil all my fun
